<i>noun</i>: 멧새 [메쌔/멛쌔] <br>
<ul>
<li><i>noun</i><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>멧새 [메쌔/멛쌔]</dt><br>
<dd>1. bunting</dd><br>
<dd>참새와 비슷하나 등에 검은 갈색의 세로무늬가 있고, 배가 약간 붉은 새.</dd><br>
<dd>A bird that is similar to a sparrow yet has a slightly red abdomen, and dark brown vertical patterns on its back.</dd><br>
<dd>2. mountain bird</dd><br>
<dd>(옛 말투로) 산에 사는 새.</dd><br>
<dd>(old-fashioned) A bird that lives on a mountain.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>